text: Arthur Bischoff (12 May 1901 - 25 August 1976) was a Swiss diver. He competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:1976 deaths Category:Swiss male divers Category:Olympic divers of Switzerland Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
